\exercise
Use the \textbf{value} command to evaluate the following expressions:
\<close>

value  "1 + (2::nat)"
value  "1 + (2::int)"
value  "1 - (2::nat)"
value  "1 - (2::int)"
value  "[a,b] @ [c,d]"

